This paper is about deep learning-based chatbot models, which are a subfield of natural language processing and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with the study of computational aspects of natural language and the design of algorithms for processing natural language data. Other likely categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SD (Software Engineering), as these fields are closely related to the development and application of deep learning-based chatbot models.
